(18, 'Busy Stampers: Scrap-booking gifts', 'add title', 'Two passionate craftswomen behind this set-up in Mumbai based online store to showcase and sell their unique handmade products.', 'http://busystampers.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/stampers.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(23, 'SL5 Mortgages', 'add title', 'add description', 'http://www.sl5mortgages.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/sl5-1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(15, 'Hakim Joint Replacement: Orthopedic Clinic in Plano, Texas', 'add title', 'add description', 'http://hakimjointreplacement.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/hakim3.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(7, 'Zinc Fitness: A premier fitness studio in London', 'Logo design, Web design', 'The brief was to make a website that stands out with a different layout. Created a grid of images on the home page to quiet an interesting effect. All studio images used on the site were touched up and  edited by us for maximum effect on the site. ', 'http://www.zincfitness.co.uk/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/zinc.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(8, 'Innocent Times: Preschool &amp; Daycare Center at Pune', 'add title', 'Visually appealing yet informative site.', 'http://www.innocenttimes.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/i_times1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(10, 'Tuscany Terraces: A resort at Neral, near Mumbai', 'add title', 'The site had to do justice to the beauty of this resort through images balanced with information through text/content since this client is introducing the concept of \\&#039;fractional ownership\\&#039; for the first time in India.', 'http://www.tuscanyterraces.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/tuscany.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(9, 'Canadian Insurance Group of Brokers', 'add title', 'The CGIB site announces all it\\&#039;s up-coming events on the site. It had to be easy to update and easy to navigate.', 'http://cgib.ca/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/cgib2.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(25, 'Golden Rules of Travel: Recommendations for amazing travel experiences', 'add title', 'add description', 'http://www.goldenrulesoftravel.com', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/golden_rules1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(12, 'HIT 95 FM: The only english FM Channel in Delhi', 'add title', 'Delhi\\&#039;s #1 Hit Music Radio: That\\&#039;s their tagline and we knew the site had to match up! Ease of constant updations, a downloads section, ability to read and hear the latest in the music world are some of the key \\&quot;features\\&quot; on the site.', 'http://hit95fm.in/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/hit95fm.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(13, 'About Us, the founders of Ajency', 'add title', 'Anuj and Avanti, the founders, pride themselves on being the \\&quot;no bullshit\\&quot; kind of people. They operate out of Goa but spend most late nights servicing clients across various time zones!', 'http://www.ajency.in/webdesign-company/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/new_logo_banner1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(26, 'Firefly Global', 'add title', 'add description', 'http://www.fireflyglobal.com', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/firefly.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(6, 'FxMentor: To learn the art of forex trading!', 'Logo Design, Web design, Website copy, Online bookings', 'Logo Design, Web design, Website copy, Online bookings', 'http://www.fxmentor.co.uk/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/fxmentor1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(17, 'Turtle: An online start-up selling accessories for women in Mumbai.', '', '', 'http://gototurtle.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/turtle2.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(22, 'Why Us?', 'add title', 'We give you enough reasons to choose us over other digital agencies. We like to keep things simple and the difference in our approach will be obvious soon after we have had our first discussion.', 'http://www.ajency.in/no-bullshit/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/why_us.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(16, 'Dojo Skins: Laptop skins in US', '', '', 'http://www.dojoskins.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/dojo.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(21, 'Vote for Kindness', 'add title', 'Making a site for this candidate was as \\&#039;eventful\\&#039; as the actual elections! Thinking the concept through was the best part of this project, because it had to be thoroughly integrated with the campaign\\&#039;s Facebook activity.', 'http://www.voteforkindness.org/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/vfk.jpg', '1', 'url', '#'),
(4, 'What we do', 'Services offered by Ajency.in', 'At Ajency we handle the complete online presence for our clients. To put it simply we design it, we build it and we market it..Having said that majority of our work is the in webdesign and web development space. Our online marketing portfolio is small albeit growing.\r\n', 'http://www.ajency.in/digital-agency-india/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/services1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(5, 'DanceSport India', 'A dance school based out of Mumbai India', 'We have been working on all aspects of Dancesport\\&#039;s online presence from their inception and have consistently filled up their batches using clever and effective online marketing. ', 'http://www.dancesportindia.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/dsi.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(11, 'Flying Elvi: A team of sky divers in Las Vegas', 'add title', 'Making the site for this enthusiastic sky diving team gave us an adrenaline rush. Next step: to experience sky diving ourselves!', 'http://flyingelvi.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Untitled.jpg', '1', 'url', '#'),
(14, 'Telcom Solutions: Telecom infrastructure and services', 'add title', 'add description', 'http://www.telcomsolutions.co.in/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/telcom3.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(20, 'Haskins Group: Social Media company focussed on the Healthcare Industry, US', 'add title', '', 'http://haskinsgroup.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/haskins3.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
(24, 'Questcare', 'add title', 'add description', 'http://www.questcareurgent.com/', 'http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/questcare1.png', '1', 'url', '#'),
