(89, 'widget_text', 'a:8:{i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:807:"<div class="onethird">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="widget-container">\r\n<h3 class="widget-title">[icon number=624 size=48] A unique satisfaction guarantee</h3>\r\n<p align="justify">This is not a promise but a guarantee. If you do not like or approve the design, we return the advance amount. There is no limit on the number of iterations we do. We want you to get a site you absolutely love. Period.</p></li>\r\n\r\n<li class="widget-container widget_text last-child">\r\n<h3 class="widget-title">[icon number=626 size=48] Honest and Affordable Pricing</h3>\r\n<p align="justify">Ajency is a lean team and everyone earns their income by doing ''real'' work. This means you get quality at a price that\r\nis often difficult to match. Pick the phone and call us; you will be surprised to hear how affordable we are. </p></ul>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:798:"<div class="onethird">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class="widget-container">\r\n<h3 class="widget-title">[icon number=625 size=48] Experienced team (no ''cheap labor'')</h3>\r\n<p align="justify">Ajency''s founding team works on every project. These are designers & coders with degrees in brand management, engineering & marketing. The exposure/ experience they bring in ensures your site delivers on its promise.</p></li>\r\n\r\n<li class="widget-container widget_text last-child">\r\n<h3 class="widget-title">[icon number=627 size=48] Blunt, direct and transparent</h3>\r\n<p align="justify">If you don''t need a website and your objectives could be met with a Facebook page instead, we will tell you that. We do not hide behind jargon or technology and make promises we can keep. Call us and find out for sure. </p></ul>\r\n</div>";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:4;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:30:"We work in a truly flat world!";s:4:"text";s:71:"<img src="http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/new_map.png">";s:6:"filter";b:0;}i:5;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"