(97, 1, '2012-02-05 22:29:09', '2012-02-05 16:59:09', '<p style="text-align: justify;">At Ajency we handle the complete online presence for our clients. To put it simply we design it, we build it and we market it. Having said that majority of our work is in the webdesign and web development space. Our online marketing portfolio is small albeit growing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Corporate Websites:</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Need a website that does justice to your company and what it stands for? Want a website that has features like blog, is easy to find on search engines, integrates with your facebook/twitter account and can be edited/updated by you without having to get in touch with a programmer?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Some features of corporate websites:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>No limit on number of pages. We do not charge by the page.</li>\r\n	<li>No extra charges for setting up a blog.</li>\r\n	<li>Complete training to edit pages and add new ones. We can maintain the site for you if you wish.</li>\r\n	<li>Free hosting for the first year.</li>\r\n	<li>Free email accounts with more than 7GB space per email id. Upto 50 email ids.</li>\r\n	<li>Photo slide shows, video support, contact form, polls, surveys etc. come as part of package.</li>\r\n	<li>Any other features you need for your corporate website are available on demand at little or no extra cost.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>E-Commerce Websites:</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Need an online store? Want to sell products online, create an online catalogue or sell digital downloads. We can create great looking stores that do not cost the world and are hassle free to manage. Some of the highlights of our e-commerce websites</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Quick turnaround time. We can have the store ready in less than a week.</li>\r\n	<li>Featured products, related products, discounts, membership and clubs, product slide show and many other modules.</li>\r\n<li>Social features like "Share discount" where a customer can get a small discount for sharing his purchase on Facebook, there by increasing reach for your site</li>\r\n	<li>Payment gateway integration with PayPal, CC Avenue or any other gateway of your choice.</li>\r\n	<li>Search engine friendly product pages.</li>\r\n	<li>All other standard e-commerce site features.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h5>Other Websites:</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Need a website for your alumni? A social network for your community? Need a personal blog that stands out from the rest? Get in touch with us for these and any other kind of websites that you need.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Online Marketing</h5>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Search Engine Optimization, Social media, Google ads and Email campaigns form the core of all online marketing activities. Each is a specialized function and is often handled by separate individuals or firms leading to disjoint marketing. </p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">At Ajency we manage the complete online presence for some of our clients and are selectively adding new ones. While we are not the go to team if you want SEO for 1000''s of phrases or Google Ads with a budget that has many zeroes; we are best equipped to act as the marketing team for local businesses, retailers, online stores and startups. </p>\r\n\r\n', 'What we do', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'digital-agency-india', '', '', '2012-02-23 23:39:50', '2012-02-23 18:09:50', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?page_id=97', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(99, 1, '2012-02-05 22:43:29', '2012-02-05 17:13:29', '<h5>[imageframe width=210 height=158 pattern="1" align="left" alt="Webdesign company Panjim"]http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/office.jpg[/imageframe]About Ajency</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We are a small (call us<a title="Boutique Web Design company" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boutique" target="_blank"> boutique</a> if you like) digital agency and we intend to stay that way. We have a lean team that is led by the Ajency founders Anuj &amp; Avanti. We operate out of a beautiful hilltop bungalow in <a title="Web design company Panjim" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Panaji" target="_blank">Panjim</a>, Goa. We also maintain a sales presence in Mumbai and Pune and are there every month. To cater to our clients in other time zones we have a sales representative based out of <a title="Webdesign company Boulder, Colarado" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boulder,_Colorado" target="_blank">Boulder, Colarado</a>.</p>\r\n</br>\r\n<h4>Ajency Founders:</h4><b>(We are open to fancy titles. Please mail us your suggestions!)</b>\r\n<h5><a href="http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/left_small.png"><img src="http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/left_small.png" alt="Webdesigner Goa" title="Anuj Khurana" width="180" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-195" rel="gallery[modal]"/></a>Anuj Khurana</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">He fancies himself as the ''left'' brain of Ajency and spends most of his time writing php code or fixing CSS bugs. A computer science engineer and a post graduate in Branding and Communications Management from <a title="Web designer &amp; marketing" href="http://www.mica.ac.in/mode/home" target="_blank">MICA Ahmedabad</a>, he has worked with more tech start-ups than we can list here. He leads sales but hates to be called a ''Suit'' and writes code but refuses to be labeled a ''geek''. Connect with him on <a title="Anuj Khurana" href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/anujkhurana" target="_blank">Linkedin</a></p>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5><a href="http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/right_small.png"><img src="http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/right_small.png" alt="Webdesigner Goa" title="Avanti Hiremath" width="180" class="alignright size-full wp-image-196" rel="gallery[modal]"/></a> Avanti Hiremath</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">She is the ‘doer’ at Ajency. She owns and runs the design &amp; operations at Ajency, which makes her the busiest body at work. Prior to Ajency, she spent her time helping multinationals like Citigroup, Venkateshwara Hatcheries and Alexandria U.S.A do a good job of managing their brand building and marketing activities. Avanti is an MBA from PICT Pune. Connect with her on <a title="Avanti Hiremath" href="http://in.linkedin.com/in/avantihiremath">Linkedin</a> </p>\r\n\r\n', 'Who we are', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'webdesign-company', '', '', '2012-02-07 10:36:47', '2012-02-07 05:06:47', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?page_id=99', 0, 'page', '', 0),
