(109, 1, '2012-02-05 23:16:09', '2012-02-05 17:46:09', '<p style="text-align: justify;">At AJency, it is our constant endeavour to create beautifully crafted websites that are efficient and affordable. Whether you are a large organization or a start-up, we have website packages for all needs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The question<strong> </strong>is: What kind of website do you need?</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Corporate Websites:</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Need a website that does justice to your company and what it stands for? Want a website that has features like blog, is easy to find on search engines, integrates with your facebook/twitter account and can be edited/updated by you without having to get in touch with a programmer?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Some features of corporate websites:</p>\r\n<div class="bullet-plus noborder">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>No limit on number of pages. We do not charge by the page.</li>\r\n	<li>No extra charges for setting up a blog.</li>\r\n	<li>Complete training to edit pages and add new ones. We can maintain the site for you if you wish.</li>\r\n	<li>Free hosting for the first year.</li>\r\n	<li>Free email accounts with more than 7GB space per email id. Upto 50 email ids.</li>\r\n	<li>Photo slide shows, video support, contact form, polls, surveys etc. come as part of package.</li>\r\n	<li>Any other features you need for your corporate website are available on demand at little or no extra cost.</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<a name="W1"></a>\r\n<h2>E-Commerce Websites:</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Need an online store? Want to sell products online, create an online catalogue or sell digital downloads. We can create great looking stores that do not cost the world and are hassle free to manage. Some of the highlights of our e-commerce websites</p>\r\n<div class="bullet-plus noborder">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Quick turnaround time â€“ We can have the store ready in less than a week.</li>\r\n	<li>Featured products, related products, discounts, membership and clubs, product slide show and many other modules.</li>\r\n	<li>Payment gateway integration with PayPal, CC Avenue or any other gateway of your choice.</li>\r\n	<li>Search engine friendly product pages.</li>\r\n	<li>All other standard e-commerce site features.</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<h2>Other Websites:</h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Need a website for your alumni? A social network for your community? Need a personal blog that stands out from the rest? Get in touch with us for these and any other kind of websites that you need.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Have a look at our portfolio to get a sense of the kind of websites we do.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We are quite convinced that we offer a superior experience for our clients. This conviction comes from our experience with other vendors as clients and now having our own clients. Donâ€™t take our word for it. Speak to our existing clients; they are the best advertising we have. To speak to any of our clients from our portfolio write in to us and we shall set up a call.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Meanwhile do read through topÂ reasons why we have been adding projects as fast as we can do them.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>â€˜Boutiqueâ€™</strong></h3>\r\n<address style="text-align: justify;">A small business offering specialized products and services.</address>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We are small, proud of it and intend to stay that way. You know upfront who is going to do your website and who is going to write the copy. We are not in the business of getting projects and having college kids on the payroll to execute on them.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>We answer the phone</strong></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ever been just plain disappointed by service professionals? Let us describe how we go the extra mile for you. Available on phone â€“ like consultants should be.Â Every call we get from you, weâ€™ll answer within 4 hours via phone, and on the rare occasion when weâ€™re on-site or helping other clients, via email.Â We put aside 1 hour per week (regardless of other conversations weâ€™ve had with you) to discuss our progress together. That way, we can explore opportunities that reveal themselves to us as we go along. Weâ€™ve learned over time that giving you this time makes you a happy customer, and helps us understand your needs better. Remember, our goal is customer service â€“ feel the joy of working with someone who lets you know whatâ€™s going on!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>One stop shop</strong></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Weâ€™re a One-Stop shop. Weâ€™ll take you start to finish in online marketing. Our goal at AJency is to give you the comprehensive solution to your online marketing needs. Donâ€™t hire a One-Trick Pony. Well, for one, SEO (or SEM) is not Internet marketing. SEO is just one solution to a specific need â€“ rankings and traffic. SEO alone often doesnâ€™t work. If you hire just an SEO specialist, this is what youâ€™ll get: Increased traffic to your website, but not necessarily any increase in sales. You want a person on your side who thinks of the big picture:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li>A know-how for all internet marketing tactics</li>\r\n	<li>A wide-angle view of all successful online strategies</li>\r\n	<li>Brilliant direction in what you need</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Why settle for an online marketer who only has a few tools, when you can get them all? You want an Internet marketing consultant who thinks of everything. A total solution for your Internet marketing needs. Looking at the big picture means you pay less.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<li>It helps you integrate your marketing so you donâ€™t do things twice</li>\r\n	<li>It means you need to hire one company instead of many</li>\r\n	<li>It helps you understand all the steps for success so you donâ€™t waste money.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Focus on small business and start-ups</strong></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We like to work with small businesses and start-ups as we get to work directly with the owners/founders. Honestly it suits our style and helps us deliver on results in a short time frame. We too are a small business, so we understand the challenges that small business owners face when bringing their business to the web. From securing your domain and hosting to deciding which payment processors to use, weâ€™re here walk you through it all.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Affordable</strong></h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We are new in the business and are committed to making it a success. Our introductory prices are a steal. We offer you the ultimate price challenge. Bring the best quote you have and we will better that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">At AJency, we constantly strive to offer affordable solutions. We make use of open source technologies, reduce over heads, work hard and pass on the benefits to our customers. It is difficult to have standardized packages especially when each client has unique needs. One needs a logo, other needs SEO and the third is not sure what he needs but wants it all! We shall offer you a custom quote once we speak to you and have understood your requirements. In the meanwhile, you can look at our rate card below to get a ballpark figure.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Website packages â€“ Start at Rs.20,000/- ($450)</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Including domain name, hosting for first year, basic SEO, design, development- Rs.20,000 ($450) onwards. No hidden costs, no surprises.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Search Engine optimization â€“ Starts at Rs.5000/- ($125)Â a month</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Search engine optimization efforts are determined by variety of variables including number of keywords to be targeted, competition, number of pages on the site, age of domain, current rankings etc. We charge a minimum of Rs.5000 a month and take up projects for a minimum of 6 months.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Google Adwords â€“ Starts at Rs.5000/- ($125) a month</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Want someone to market your site online? We shall help you budget for it, execute it and give you regular reports so you know how your marketing money is performing. We also create microsites for the campaigns and ensure effective lead generation from your site. Google Adwords packages start from Rs.5000 a month. Minimum duration of projects is 3 months.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Social media marketing â€“ Starts at Rs.5000/- ($125) a month</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our social media packages include maintaining your Facebook, Twitter and other social networking profiles. Blogging packages are also available. We start at monthly outgo of Rs.5000 for a minimum of 6 months.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Content writing â€“ Starts at Rs.1000/- ($25) per article</strong></h2>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">For effective website copy, case studies, white papers, articles, press releases, do contact us. We have some gifted writers on our panel and we are keen to work with you on the same. The cost of article is determined by domain, length and purpose. Minimum of Rs.1000 per article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Are you based outside of India? The founding team of Ajency has worked extensively on international projects and has been on distributed teams spread across multiple time zones. Here are some of the reasons why you should consider them for your website and online needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;">Dollar - Rupee arbitrage:</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Dollar is a much stronger currency than the Indian rupee. This allows you to get more value for your money spent in India. One dollar is approximately equal to 50 Indian Rupees. This means that what costs approximately $2000 to do in your country, will cost a fraction (approximately $500) in India.Â  It''s the same logic that some of the biggest internet companies like Yahoo, Google, AOL, Microsoft, Ebay and others use when they build web teams in India.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;">No compromise on quality:</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Low cost does not mean low quality. Have a look at our <a href="http://www.ajency.in/web-design-portfolio/" target="_self">portfolio</a> to see our quality of work. We have worked with customers in numerous countries (U.S and Europe) and have a fair understanding of the quality and detailing required.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;">Communication:</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Everyone at Ajency is quite lucid in English (written and spoken). With the use of messenger, Skype and Email, you will find it is more efficient to work with a remote team than one that requires frequent meetings and phone calls.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\nAre you based outside of India? The founding team of Ajency has worked extensively on international projects and has been on distributed teams spread across multiple time zones. Here are some of the reasons why you should consider them for your website and online needs.\r\n<h3>Dollar - Rupee arbitrage:</h3>\r\nDollar is a much stronger currency than the Indian rupee. This allows you to get more value for your money spent in India. One dollar is approximately equal to 50 Indian Rupees. This means that what costs approximately $2000 to do in your country, will cost a fraction (approximately $500) in India.Â  It''s the same logic that some of the biggest internet companies like Yahoo, Google, AOL, Microsoft, Ebay and others use when they build web teams in India.\r\n<h3>No compromise on quality:</h3>\r\nLow cost does not mean low quality. Have a look at our portfolio to see our quality of work. We have worked with customers in numerous countries (U.S and Europe) and have a fair understanding of the quality and detailing required.\r\n<h3>Communication:</h3>\r\nEveryone at Ajency is quite lucid in English (written and spoken). With the use of messenger, Skype and Email, you will find it is more efficient to work with a remote team than one that requires frequent me\r\netings and phone calls.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWith the same energy and passion as you do! </br>Your site will be far more than just text and images, and will include features that add interactivity.', 'Temp page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'temp-page', '', '', '2012-02-05 23:22:04', '2012-02-05 17:52:04', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?page_id=109', 0, 'page', '', 0),
