(144, 1, '2012-02-06 02:41:57', '2012-02-05 21:11:57', '<p style="text-align: justify;">[imageframe width=185 height=185 pattern="1" align="left" alt="Cuts through the bullsit"]http://www.ajency.in/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/no_bs.png[/imageframe]Ajency.in offers creative, cost effective website design and online marketing. We do it with honesty, humor and do it in plain speak. Or as our tagline goes "We cut through the bullshit".</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">"Bullshit" has long been used by those in the know to get the client to agree to what they want. This is especially true with technology due to lack of knowledge, and in design &amp; marketing due to the intuitive nature of the domain. At Ajency we keep things simple and the difference in our approach will be obvious soon after we have had our first discussion.</p>\r\n</br>\r\n<b>Read through the top reasons why we have been adding projects as fast as we can do them.</b>\r\n\r\n<div class="onehalf"><h5> [icon number=624 size=48] A unique satisfaction guarantee</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">This is not a promise but a guarantee. If you do not like or approve the design, we return the advance amount. There is no limit on the number of iterations we do. We want you to get a site you absolutely love. Period.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="onehalf onehalflast"><h5> [icon number=626 size=48] Honest and Affordable Pricing</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ajency is a lean team and everyone earns their income by doing ''real'' work. This means you get quality at a price that is often difficult to match. Pick the phone and call us; you will be surprised to hear how affordable we are.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="onehalf"><h5>[icon number=625 size=48] Experienced team (no ''cheap labor'')</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The team that founded Ajency works on every single project. These are designers and coders with degrees in brand management, engineering &amp; marketing. The exposure and experience they bring in ensures your site delivers on its promise.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="onehalf onehalflast"><h5>[icon number=627 size=48] Blunt, direct and transparent</h5>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">If you don''t need a website and your objectives could be met with a Facebook page instead, we will tell you that. We do not hide behind jargon or technology and make promises we can keep. Call us and find out for sure.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Why Choose Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'no-bullshit', '', '', '2012-02-18 11:18:27', '2012-02-18 05:48:27', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?page_id=144', 0, 'page', '', 1),
