(246, 1, '2012-02-17 17:54:10', '2012-02-17 12:24:10', '<p style="text-align: justify;">We are always on the lookout for team members who can add to the joys of working at Ajency.in. All it takes is the right attitude, the willingness to learn and work hard (not to be confused with long hours!) and the right skill set. As a digital agency we seek individuals who can help us create effective online presence for our clients. You could do this with design, HTML &amp; CSS, PHP, mobile app development, Wordpress, Client servicing, Search Engine Optimization (SEO), Social media or copy writing.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We are based out of Panjim, Goa and are looking for candidates from in and around or those who are willing to relocate.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Work hours: 9.30 A.M to 6.30 P.M | Monday to Friday.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">For all job applications or to initiate a dialogue around working with Ajency, write in to us at <a href="mailto:workwithus@ajency.in" target="_blank">workwithus@ajency.in</a>.</p>\r\nAt the moment we are aggressively hiring for the following positions:\r\n\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.ajency.in/mobile-developers/" target="_blank">Mobile developers</a></h4>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.ajency.in/visual-designer/" target="_blank">Visual Designers</a></h4>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.ajency.in/web-designer/" target="_blank">Web Designer</a></h4>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.ajency.in/web-programmer/" target="_blank">Web Programmer</a></h4>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.ajency.in/search-engine-optimization-seo-specialist/" target="_blank">Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Specialist</a></h4>\r\n<h4><a href="http://www.ajency.in/social-media-marketing/" target="_blank">Social Media Marketing</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Work with Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'careers', '', '', '2013-04-23 17:23:22', '2013-04-23 11:53:22', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?page_id=246', 0, 'page', '', 0),
