(341, 1, '2012-05-31 12:55:41', '2012-05-31 07:25:41', '<p style="text-align: justify;">We are looking for a web programmer with expertise in PHP and especially Wordpress CMS. At Ajency we are heavily invested in Wordpress as our choice of platform and need an individual who can without much supervision handle all our wordpress coding needs. </p>\r\n<h5>Who are we looking for?</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">You are someone who can write plugins, code html pages into wordpress themes and edit existing plugins and themes.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Experience as a web developer: 0-5 years. Your role and profile will depend on the current comfort level with development and experience.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">A degree in computers is desirable.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Preferably PHP experience. Dot Net developers looking to move to LAMP stack are welcome as well. Experience with open source CMS like Wordpress, Joomla, Drupal helps.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Javascript expertise will pretty much guarantee an offer from us!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Remuneration and perks</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Salary offered is best in class. Expect a nice hike from your existing income.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Laptop + Data cards are the norm for every member of the team. We also give each new joinee a fixed purse to do up their work space. Whether you buy ergonomic keyboards or your own personal mini fridge is totally your call :)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'Web Programmer', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'web-programmer', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:12:23', '2014-04-17 08:42:23', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=341', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(346, 1, '2012-05-31 13:06:16', '2012-05-31 07:36:16', '\r\n<h5>Who are we looking for?</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Primary skill-set required is strong written and spoken English communication skills.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">If you have worked with online marketing tools like Google Adwords, Google Analytics, Search Engine Optimization then you are already half way through! If you haven''t we will train you.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">One of our major clients is a UK based financial management company. So if words like funds, stocks, GDP don''t scare your and bore you then the chances of you enjoying the job are higher.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Having a degree in business studies (BMS/M.B.A) or commerce and accounting (B.Com) or literature will help.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Though we are open to applications from graduates and post graduates from all streams, and prior experience is not a requirement; the role and responsibility will depend on your prior experience and educational background initially. Rest we will let your work decide your growth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Remuneration and perks</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Salary offered is best in class. Expect a nice hike from your existing income.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Laptop + Data cards are the norm for every member of the team. We also give each new joinee a fixed purse to do up their work space. Whether you buy ergonomic keyboards or your own personal mini fridge is totally your call :)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Job ID: AJ2401</h5>', 'Social Media Marketing', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'social-media-marketing', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:12:27', '2014-04-17 08:42:27', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=346', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(348, 1, '2012-05-31 14:15:39', '2012-05-31 08:45:39', '<p style="text-align: justify;">We are looking for a SEO and Adwords professional to work on our online presence as well as for client projects. Your focus areas will be:\r\n<ul class="pointinglist">\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Keyword research</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Google Adwords account management</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">On site optimization using meta tags and copy editing</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Link building using blogs, online directories and white hat techniques.</li>\r\n</ul> </p>\r\n<h5>Who are we looking for?</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Minimum of two years experience with SEO.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Experience with adwords is preferred but not a requirement. We will train you on Google adwords.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Should be able to add the meta tags using basic HTML.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Strong written and spoken communication skills are a requirement.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">An MBA in marketing will help.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Remuneration and perks</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Salary offered is best in class. Expect a nice hike from your existing income.</li>\r\n<li style="text-align: justify;">Laptop + Data cards are the norm for every member of the team. We also give each new joinee a fixed purse to do up their work space. Whether you buy ergonomic keyboards or your own personal mini fridge is totally your call :)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5>Job ID: 2402</h5>', 'Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Specialist', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'search-engine-optimization-seo-specialist', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:12:32', '2014-04-17 08:42:32', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=348', 0, 'post', '', 0),
