(464, 1, '2012-07-26 03:34:08', '2012-07-25 22:04:08', 'Homestay in Kolad, near Mumbai.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nA 3-3.5 hour drive from Mumbai or Pune, Good Heavens is a perfect weekend getaway. One can do lots here, or not do anything at all – that depends on what kind of a holiday you are looking for. It can be action packed with activities like White Water Rafting, Trekking, Camping, Rock Climbing, Rappelling, Kayaking etc. or if you simply want to chill out and recharge yourself, you can spend some peaceful time by the river.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.goodheavens.in/">Visit site</a>', 'Good Heavens', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'good-heavens', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:11:46', '2014-04-17 08:41:46', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=464', 0, 'post', '', 0),
