(483, 1, '2012-10-16 16:09:54', '2012-10-16 10:39:54', 'Intellidocs is a cloud based document management system<!--more-->, with emphasis on document security and access control. The service allows organizations to grant and revoke access to documents and folders. The users access the documents on their personal or organization provided tablets like iPad or Android based tablets. The service/app was built for Wasp Technologies, who in turn is deploying it with numerous organizations in Ireland.\r\n\r\nThe app was built using Sencha and Phonegap and allows us to build once and deploy on multiple platforms. This significantly reduces the project complexity and cost.\r\n\r\nThe app is proprietary; if you wish to get a demo, then get in touch with us and we will send you a build for your iPad or Android tablet. Write in to <a href="mailto:anuj@ajency.in">anuj@ajency.in</a> if you would like something similar developed.', 'Intellidocs.net', 'Intellidocs is a cloud based document management system, that allows organizations to grant and revoke access to documents and folders.', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'intellidocs-net', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:10:26', '2014-04-17 08:40:26', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=483', 0, 'post', '', 0),
