(486, 1, '2012-10-16 16:44:27', '2012-10-16 11:14:27', 'A paid health and fitness platform that allows members to work out from home<!--more--> with personalized assistance from a trainer and nutritionist. The site allows you to keep track of your meals, diet plans, workout routine, interact with other community members over a Q&amp;A forum, and have personalized interaction with the trainer and nutritionist.\r\n\r\nThe site saw over a 1000 registrations in the first month of its launch and new features are being added every week.\r\n\r\nThe site is built using Wordpress + Buddypress and an iOS app for mobile interface is in the works using Sencha and Phonegap.', 'WesleyVirgin.com', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wesleyvirgin-com', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:10:19', '2014-04-17 08:40:19', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=486', 0, 'post', '', 0),
