(493, 1, '2012-10-16 17:08:29', '2012-10-16 11:38:29', 'A social network for the fraternities and sororities for US based universities.<!--more--> The idea has already won a <a href="http://www.utk.edu/tntoday/2012/05/16/undergraduate-business-plan-competition/" target="_blank"> business plan competition</a> and Ajency.in is the design and development partner for it. \r\n\r\nThe site is being built using Wordpress Network (earlier known as Wordpress multiuser). There are only a few dozen teams across the World who have experience on this platform.\r\n\r\nThe project is being built on LAMP stack on the server, HTML5 and CSS3 on the browser and an iOS app using Sencha and PhoneGap.\r\n\r\nDo get in touch with us at <a href="mailto:anuj@ajency.in">anuj@ajency.in</a> if you would like to get something similar developed.', 'GreekConnect.com', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'greekconnect-com', '', '', '2014-04-17 14:10:11', '2014-04-17 08:40:11', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/?p=493', 0, 'post', '', 0),
