(162, 0, 'cc_slide1_title', 'Retirement Planning', 'yes'),
(163, 0, 'cc_slide1_content', '<p>While all of us would like to retire comfortably, the complexity and time required in building a successful retirement plan can make the whole process seem nothing short of daunting. However, it can often be done with fewer headaches (and financial pain) than you might think - all it takes is a little homework, an attainable savings and investment plan, and a long-term commitment.</p>', 'yes'),
(164, 0, 'cc_slide1_images', 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/retirement-planning_new.jpg', 'yes'),
(165, 0, 'cc_slide1_url', 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=2', 'yes'),
(166, 0, 'cc_slide2_title', 'Life Insurance', 'yes'),
(167, 0, 'cc_slide2_content', '<p>There are many reasons for life insurance. What are yours? Protect your family and your loved ones. We are a broker for over 40 well known Life insurance carriers so we can help find the best available coverage at the right price.</p>', 'yes'),
(168, 0, 'cc_slide2_images', 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/life_insurance_new.jpg', 'yes'),
(169, 0, 'cc_slide2_url', 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=2', 'yes'),
(170, 0, 'cc_slide3_title', 'Long Term Care', 'yes'),
(171, 0, 'cc_slide3_content', 'Custom Text', 'yes'),
(172, 0, 'cc_slide3_contenttext', '<p>Most of us will buy health insurance and insurance for home, car and other property replacement. However, few people think to buy long-term care insurance, and assume that their savings will be sufficient to meet any associated expenses. In fact, long-term care can be very expensive and can deplete a lifetime of savings within a few years.</p>', 'yes'),
(173, 0, 'cc_slide3_images', 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/longterm.png', 'yes'),
(174, 0, 'cc_slide3_url', 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=2', 'yes'),
(175, 0, 'cc_slide4_title', 'Annuity', 'yes'),
(176, 0, 'cc_slide4_content', 'Custom Text', 'yes'),
(177, 0, 'cc_slide4_contenttext', '<p>Annuities can be structured according to a wide array of details and factors, such as the duration of time that payments from the annuity can be guaranteed to continue. Annuities can be created so that, upon annuitization, payments will continue so long as either the annuitant or their spouse is alive. Alternatively, annuities can be structured to pay out funds for a fixed amount of time, such as 20 years, regardless of how long the annuitant lives.</p>', 'yes'),
