(440, 1, '2012-01-03 08:01:27', '2012-01-03 08:01:27', '<h4>Where do you want to take your business?</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">What are the key issues and concerns your business is facing? Is your current strategy in line with the growth objectives and future vision? If not, then probably its time to re-look and analyze your long-term business objectives and strategies.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Thomas Watson Jr. said, â€œGood Design is Good Businessâ€.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">As a Global Design Consulting Company, we design and develop cutting-edge, reliable, high-quality design solutions and value-added professional services. These provide customers around the world with smarter ways to be productive and competitive. Our expertise in enabling our customers to manifest and leverage their core business objectives by strategic innovation and design interventions, enhance performances, resulting into business growth and efficiencies.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Innovation is our passion, and your needs our guiding force. Lokusdesign delivers high performance expertise in focused verticals like Strategic design, product and packaging design, brand consulting and graphic design, Architecture, interiors and retail design. Our proprietary processes, services and excellent team capabilities fuel growth; equip businesses, brands and products with unmatched competitive advantage.\r\nOur innovative and aesthetic solutions enable you achieve brand goals, larger mindshare and product appreciation.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="accordion">\r\n<h3><a href="#">Strategy</a></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6>Branding and Communication Strategy:</h6>\r\nInsights research, strategy, branding, communication design, styling, values, vision, personality, overall experience, differentiation, positioning, evolution or revolution, etc.\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><a href="#">Branding</a></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6>Corporate Identity Design:</h6>\r\nIdentity design, logo, naming, theme creation, color story, shape, tactile/ materials, sound, illustration, typography, environment, house styling, collateral, brand manual, etc.\r\n<h6>Graphic Design:</h6>\r\nCollateral, internal &amp; external communication, signage, exhibitions, packaging graphics, etc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><a href="#">Packaging</a></h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<h6>Packaging design innovation:</h6>\r\nStructures, form innovation, styling, themes, trends, house- styling, differentiation, retail, positioning, green design, etc.\r\n<h6>Packaging graphics:</h6>\r\nIdentity design, theme creation, color story, trends, house styling, design for decals, shrink sleeves, labels, printing\r\n<h6>Mechanism design:</h6>\r\nDispensing, pumps, atomizers, unit dosing, child resistant, non-spilling, metered dosing, tamper proof details, delivery systems, hinge design, etc.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2012-01-10 15:12:49', '2012-01-10 15:12:49', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=440', 0, 'page', '', 0, 0),
(443, 1, '2012-01-03 08:49:44', '2012-01-03 08:49:44', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Lokusdesign is a growth catalyst, providing strategic value to businesses and brands. The Design process that we adopt, is scientific, methodical and reliable, which has been successfully demonstrated for years, through our products and services. Our unidirectional, five stage seamless approach enables you and our team to:</p><ul>\r\n<li><strong> Identify:</strong> issues, trends and opportunities</li>\r\n<li><strong> Integrate:</strong> systems and processes with business objectives</li>\r\n<li><strong> Innovate:</strong> ideas, processes and solutions</li>\r\n<li><strong> Translate:</strong> ideas into reality</li>\r\n<li><strong> Maximize:</strong> potential and value</li></ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our proprietary process has the capability to turn businesses into profit centres, optimize time to market and significantly increase efficiencies. The systematic approach makes it easier for us and for our customers to understand and evaluate the success of each stage in the process, thereby reducing risks. Our process concretizes the seemingly elusive design concepts and makes them output oriented.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="accordion">\r\n<h3><a href="#">(Identify)</a></h3>\r\n<div>â€œFish are the last to recognize waterâ€ â€“ author unknown\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">To address your business concerns, we believe in getting to the root cause of a problem. Before plunging into the creative phase, we choose to pause and analyze the scenarios. Most often, a fresh perspective brings to surface, issues and opportunities which are otherwise deemed insignificant. We employ our specialist research methodologies, observational insights and proprietary analytical processes to identify needs, trends, complexities and potential failure modes, avoiding iterations and unsuccessful ideas.</p></div>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href="#">[Integrate]</a></h3>\r\n<div><p style="text-align: justify;">This stage of our proprietary process involves integration of the identified constraints, systems, functions and stake holder interests, with user needs and larger business objectives. Further filtering of these inputs, categorizing them into sectors and priorities, results into a holistic analysis. This in turn enables re-definition, convergence and synergies for robust innovation.</p></div>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href="#">{Innovate}</a></h3>\r\n<div><p style="text-align: justify;">â€œCreativity is the defeat of habit by originalityâ€ - Arthur Koestler</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Innovation though critical, is a much clichÃ©d word and easy to get carried away with. We believe that for innovation to make businessense, it needs to act as an â€œenablerâ€ rather than an â€œenhancerâ€. The key to successful innovation lies in determining what the needs are, whether it is a concept innovation, a design innovation, innovation in strategy or business, or as simple as a process innovation. Our radical Ideas, par excellence creativity and unrestricted expressions fuel high-end innovation. Our proprietary process enables us to brainstorm, think out of the box and evolve seemingly weird ideas, which are further validated and honed to result in actionable value propositions. Thereby, leading to a winning solution.</p></div>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href="#">&lt;Translate&gt;</a></h3>\r\n<div><p style="text-align: justify;">We define innovation by its possibility of translating into fast, reliable and successful solutions. Ideas or strategies are transformed into reality or practice by deploying systems, processes and resources intelligently. The virtual image is much more tangible now. This phase marks the Interpretation of expressions and experiences to spatial manifestation, features to products, core concerns to opportunities and ultimately leading to growth and value. In the process of translating the idea to reality, Lokusdesign and our Strategic Alliance Partners shows our commitment towards our clients</p></div>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href="#">*Maximise*</a></h3>\r\n<div><p style="text-align: justify;">The final stage of our process maximizes benefits and value. An effective design solution can provide diverse benefits other than addressing the immediate needs or concerns. For instance, while addressing some of the core business issues of efficiency, growth and competitiveness, our design solutions bring tremendous value and equity, enhance perception and maximize profits. These help clients and businesses, explore newer applications and affordances, penetrate new markets and positions, innovate ways to create new segments and categories, thereby creating an opportunity to become a market leader.</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4></h4>', 'How we work', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-process', '', '', '2012-01-04 07:48:24', '2012-01-04 07:48:24', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=443', 0, 'page', '', 0, 0),
(444, 1, '2012-01-03 09:01:48', '2012-01-03 09:01:48', '<li><h6>Branding and Communication Strategy:</h6>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Insights research, strategy, branding, communication design, styling, values, vision, personality, overall experience, differentiation, positioning, evolution or revolution, etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Lokusdesign works with organizations to lead their markets by revitalizing brand and product strategies. With our high performance processes we evolve existing strategies, systems and services to new levels of relevance, enabling people to experience them in entirely new ways. </p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Development of strategy starts with deep market understanding, brand and user research to uncover new opportunities that sets the stage for innovation. A new strategy is about being able to envision something that never existed before, and then make it real. Creating unprecedented opportunities for our customers involves unlimited imagination, and utilizing our expert tools and models, we create meaningful new concepts that will have a powerful impact on the consumer culture and a significant contribution to our customerâ€™s economic growth. \r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our framework to audit and align relationships between our customers and their brand, products, services and consumers make a never existing strategy real. The result is a revitalized company with innovative products and services aligned with our customerâ€™s business and brand goals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">On the way from idea to reality, these strategies are tested against business goals, return on the investment, cultural impact, and how every aspect of change is going to work in reality.</p>', 'Strategy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'strategy', '', '', '2012-01-10 07:00:19', '2012-01-10 07:00:19', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=444', 0, 'page', '', 0, 0),
(446, 1, '2012-01-03 10:38:05', '2012-01-03 10:38:05', '<ul><li><h6>Corporate Identity Programs</h6></li>\r\n<li><h6>Communication and Graphic design</h6></li></ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Brand represents a critical tool to secure and monetize customer relationships. We understand the role that brand plays in customer choice, the client''s relative brand equity, the fit between the client''s brand and the identified customer sets and opportunities, and a way to build a strong brand. Our powerful techniques trigger our Customers to think on the lines of their strengths, their competitorâ€™s weaknesses and the key drivers for performance. From analyzing their competition to defining their brand personality, we help carve out a unique communications platform and build a comprehensive communications plan that differentiates our customerâ€™s brand in the marketplace.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our thorough brand assessment is the core of our process. Every project at Lokusdesign begins with an in-depth evaluation of the current brand perception among its key stake holders. We review our customerâ€™s business strategy, vision, mission and purpose, conduct internal and external stakeholder research, audit communications practices, and assess the industry environment. These processes provide a foundation for developing and evaluating brand actions, brand architecture and defines the communication design road map.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our innovation is grounded by our expertise in brand science. We look at brands as strategic assets that need to be aligned with the company''s vision, mission and portfolio. Using our analytical tools, we enable brands to shift demand and build greater financial value.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Often, the logo is the face to a brand, giving a brand its unique identity and personality. It is a visual representation of a brandâ€™s core business strategy, its vision and values and forms a corporate signature for the company.Â  We design identity for brands that translate strategies into visual and verbal expressions of the companyâ€™s brand. We achieve this through typography, color, imagery, language and sensory stimuli including sound and texture.</p>', 'Branding', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'branding-communication-design', '', '', '2012-01-10 07:02:55', '2012-01-10 07:02:55', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=446', 0, 'page', '', 0, 0),
(447, 1, '2012-01-03 10:41:05', '2012-01-03 10:41:05', '<ul><li><h6>Packaging design innovation</h6></li>\r\n<li><h6>Packaging graphics</h6></li>\r\n<li><h6>Mechanism design</h6></li></ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Lokusdesign helps clients develop a competitive advantage with their packaging. We pride ourselves in approaching each packaging challenge with the spirit of innovation that has made our company one of the foremost design companies globally.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">We cater to packaging design needs across sectors like FMCG, Food &amp; Beverage, Health and Beauty, with our truly integrated Packaging Design Services. We consider every aspect of our customerâ€™s packaging requirements from brand equity to functionality and ultimately achieving end consumer delight. Good package design incorporates more than just placing a product in a box, but creates an instant emotional connect between the consumer and the product. Our stunning high visibility designs attract consumers in a highly cluttered retail scape and build high perception value for its Brand.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">An effective design solution considers the needs of the entire Value chain, including the Brand &amp; Marketing Strategies, Manufacturing and Logistics function; needs and mindsets of Retailers and Consumers. We develop ideas and design solutions that encompass structural aspects, printing, converting technologies, and finishing techniques. Lokusdesign with its expert processes aims at weight &amp; material optimization and affordances leading to cost advantages and maximizing profits.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Our distinctive designs, commitment to excellence and impressive portfolio are a testimony to our expertise in Packaging Design. With reliable and fast delivery cycles and customized solutions, we empower our customers to scale and faster time-to-market abilities.</p>', 'Packaging', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'packaging-design', '', '', '2012-01-10 07:18:58', '2012-01-10 07:18:58', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=447', 0, 'page', '', 0, 0),
