(453, 1, '2012-01-04 06:55:19', '2012-01-04 06:55:19', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Across the world, in practically every industry, Lokusdesign has helped customers achieve brand & business goals. From smart brand and efficient environments to intelligent products and advanced packaging. Lokusdesign has helped customers maximize value & return on investments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Lokusdesign with its high performance expertise in focused verticals, provides breakthrough solutions that fuel growth, while simultaneously equipping business, brands and products with unmatched competitive advantage. We base our success on our excellent team capabilities and proprietary processes, thereby maximizing value and return on investments. Our innovative and aesthetic solutions have enabled our clients to achieve brand goals, larger mindshare and product appreciation. The endless endeavor to create newer markets for our clients has positioned us as a valuable business partner.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>More than 80 prestigious clientsINSERT INTO `wp_snzvvf_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `orderby`) VALUES
(480, 1, '2012-01-10 14:29:45', '2012-01-10 14:29:45', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Working with the best brands, and the most challenging projects, we have created a culture of excellence at Lokusdesign. We believe in taking up responsibilities, working under Client pressures and yet delivering results that delight our Customers. Self-motivation is our key to performance, continuously expanding our horizon and striving to achieve new altitudes of excellence. Performance, Commitment and Innovation are both our goals and guiding principles. If you share this belief, then it is your chance to work for an aggressively growing, progressive and dynamic organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>Apply to <a href="mailto:careers@lokusdesign.com">careers@lokusdesign.com</a></b></p>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.ajency.in/brian/wp-content/uploads/careers.png" alt="" title="" width="600" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-481" />\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Joining Lokusdesign translates into continual opportunities to expand on what you can do. Challenge yourself with interesting work focused on delivering innovation and proven solutions. Our associates come with a wide variety of experience in the industry, added to their qualifications from the top institutes globally. However, we also recruit fresh talent out of institutes, who have the passion and potential in them to bring fresh perspectives in a business frame work.</p>\r\n \r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Be it design function, marketing, HR or other support functions, we believe in working with a self-driven talent pool and provide them exponential opportunities to grow within the company and simultaneously acquire a global experience. Working across 19 countries globally and with our offices in India, Finland and USA, you get to work on the global standards of design. Our utmost commitment is towards quality, and performance is the only way that we recognize for growth at Lokusdesign.</p>\r\n', 'Join our team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'join-our-team', '', '', '2012-01-10 14:31:39', '2012-01-10 14:31:39', '', 0, 'http://www.ajency.in/brian/?page_id=480', 0, 'page', '', 0, 0),
